<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Abu Dhabi, 22 Apr (MENA)-- The newspaper 
AL-ITTIHAD of Abu Dhabi today reports that Palestinian President 
Yasir 'Arafat will pay an urgent visit to Jordan next week to 
