<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 22 Apr (MENA)--AL-AKHBAR describes the 
United Nation's claim that it is afraid its military 
intervention against the Serbs would lead to a conflagration in 
other areas of Europe as a feeble excuse to justify its 
nonintervention. 
  In its commentary today, the paper denounces the UN Security 
