  [Text] Prime Minister Yitzhaq Rabin says a new and 
aggressive type of religious conversion has evolved in the Arab 
world, and its seeds are being felt even in the Israeli Arab 
sector. This is an extreme religious approach whose adherents 
refuse to recognize any non-Islamic political entity. This 
credo motivates the activities of Hamas and other radical 
organizations in the territories. Therefore, an arrangement 
with the PLO is the only possibility. The prime minister made 
these remarks in a meeting with kibbutzim members. 

