  [Text] India today rejected the Pakistani propaganda that 
the visit of the next group of ambassadors to Jammu and Kashmir 
is a fact-finding mission by Islamic countries. Expressing 
regret over the distorted projection by Islamabad, an External 
Affairs Ministry spokesman clarified in New Delhi that it is 
neither a group of ambassadors of Islamic countries nor is it in 
