  [Text] In occupied Kashmir, mojahedin during their stepped 
up retaliatory attacks on Indian troops killed 14 soldiers. 
Mojahedin attacked military targets in Anantnag-Islamabad and 
its adjacent areas. Six soldiers were killed in a fierce clash 
with mojahedin near Anantnag-Islamabad. Mojahedin also killed 
two Indian soldiers when they tried to besiege the Jamia Masjid 
