damaged in the attack. Indian soldiers gunned down two 
civilians during a crackdown and house-to-house search operation 
in Dayalgaon in Anantnag-Islamabad. Indian soldiers martyred 
and wounded a number of civilians in indiscriminate firing 
during siege and search operation at Batmalu in Srinagar. 

