<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Bucharest, April 23, IRNA -- Foreign Minister 'Ali 
Akbar Velayati here today reiterated the full support of the 
Iranian people and government for the oppressed people of Bosnia 
against the aggressor Serbs. 
  He made the remark in a meeting with his Bosnian counterpart 
Haris Siladzic on the sidelines of the Crans-Montana forum here, 
where the two sides also reviewed the latest developments in 
Bosnia-Herzegovina particularly the Gorazde crisis. 
