<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Judge Interrogates Ja'ja, Issues Warrant </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC2404192894 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1900 GMT 24 Apr 
94 </F>

<F P=103> NC2404192894 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Judge Munir Hunayn, the judicial investigator 
looking into the case of the assassination of Engineer Dany 
Sham'un and members of his family, questioned Samir Ja'ja' in 
the presence of his lawyer As'ad Abu-Ra'd at the Justice Palace 
at 1000 today. The interrogation lasted until 2000 this 
evening. The judicial investigator decided to issue an arrest 
warrant for Ja'ja' and referred the warrant to the public 
prosecutor at the court of cassation for implementation. 

</TEXT>

