<H3> <TI>   Governors Discuss Ban on Demonstrations </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Governors Discuss Ban on Demonstrations </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC2304170794 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1530 GMT 23 Apr 
