citizens of the decision issued by National Defense Minister 
Muhsin Dalull yesterday suspending arms licenses throughout 
Lebanon for 38 hours from Monday [25 April] evening to Wednesday 
[27 April] morning. The army command was ordered to implement 
this decision. 

