<F P=105>  Pashto </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] On 10 April a delegation of Golboddin's party, led 
by [word indistinct] Arghandiwal, head of the party's finances, 
visited Moscow. [Words indistinct] in an article with the 
headline: War Equipments for Hekmatyar, wrote that the purpose 
of the visit, which was [words indistinct] of the Russian 
